'''Estakhr''' ({{lang-fa|استخر}}) is an [[Iran|Iranian]] newspaper in the [[Fars province|Fars]] region. The [[Concessionaire]] of this newspaper was ''Mohammadhasan Bavanati'' known as ''Estakhr'' and has been published in [[Shiraz]] since 1918. <ref>Rumi,Siroos; List of printed matters of Fars;2006;[[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

